data.description: Don't miss out on this great opportunity! This now vacant home was built in 2000 making it a rare find in the city Niagara Falls. This property features many new additions to it's like-new structure such as a newer roof (2019), brand new tank-less hot water tank, brand new furnace, new vinyl windows brand new carpet in all four bedrooms, new sump pump, new water spouts, new mitigation system for radon, and new paint all through the house! This home features comfortable size living room and a very spacious eat-in kitchen with lots of counter top space and cabinets for storage. The four bedrooms are all very sizable with enough room for a king bed in each one with room to spare! The full basement has tons of room with the possibility to be finished. This house sits on a very sizable lot with a big front porch and comes with the shed in the back. Come and see this gem before it's gone.
